{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Thrown into a mysterious world bound within the pages of an ancient book, you must find your way back home. Master your spellbook to draw and cast your spells. Use them to manipulate your surroundings and solve challenging puzzles in unexpected ways.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854360/extras/Intro.gif?t=1740082815\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Draw your Spells!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore this practical glyph-based magic system. Sketch spells onto the pages of your spellbook, and cast them whenever you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854360/extras/Gif_Draw.gif?t=1740082815\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Crystals hold the key to uncovering this world\u2019s secrets. Use your spells to influence your surroundings, think outside the box and find your own way forward!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854360/extras/Puzzles.gif?t=1740082815\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Colour-blind Support</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Colours are an important part of the puzzle-solving experience, and a dedicated colour-blind support ensures every player can experience the game to its fullest</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854360/extras/Colorblind.gif?t=1740082815\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2854360?t=1740082815","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2854360?t=1740082815","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2854360/e97ef14f7004734ed9a71de622223aa0a5789dd9/capsule_231x